| translation =Tewi Inaba's theme.<br />I designed this to be a little playful, sentimental, and Japanese.<br />How is it? It came out fairly easygoing and cute, and I think it fits this [[Phantasmagoria of Flower View|kaeizuka]] to a T.<br />Actually, the notes and scales used aren't Japanese. If you were to ask me "where's the Japan in it?," I really couldn't tell you. But doesn't it seem Japanese?
