| translation =The staff roll theme.<br />I thought about making a lighter staff roll than normal, but I regret making it both light and almost empty. Like I should have made one of those two stand out.<br />Well, I hope it has a sense of closure. But, it also feels like a beginning to me. It's not bad, right?
}}

