|titleEN  =The Forgotten Eternal Starlight
|comment  ={{lang|zh|东方惯例的标题曲。      ※作曲：文件

在东方标题曲特有的旋律上进行了改动，不过这样一来旋律似乎就不明显了。<br>整体风格略为阴暗，似乎和积极向上（？）的主题不符？}}
|translation = Title screen theme       ※Composer: 文件

A variation of [[Theme of Eastern Story|the unique motif]] in Touhou's menu theme, but now it feels like the melody doesn't stand out any more.<br>
The whole piece feels a little downcast. Maybe it doesn't fit the game's positive(?) theme?
}}

{{MusicRoom
|category =Stage 1 theme
|title    ={{lang|zh|宁静夏夜的微风}}
|titleEN  =A Peaceful Summer Night's Breeze
|comment  ={{lang|zh|1面的主题曲。      ※作曲：11

因为是夏夜的微风，所以开头做成了格外静谧的感觉。<br>这样的开始之后，才是渐渐地进入了游戏。<br>旋律是怎么写出来的，其实我也不知道。<br>仅仅是在脑海中突然出现了这段后赶紧记录下来罢了，效果却意外的好呢。}}
|translation =Stage 1 theme       ※Composer: 11

Because it's a summer night's breeze, I made the beginning very calm.<br>After the beginning, it flows with the game's pace.<br>Truthfully, I don't know how the melody came to me.<br>It just popped up in my head, and I hurriedly wrote it down, but it seems to be unexpectedly nice.
}}

