一首自始自终都很悠闲自由的曲子，尤其是在旋律上随心所欲的发挥。<br>在悠闲之余，还延续了前一面的静谧。<br>整首曲子莫名其妙的就做成了钢琴曲。<br>不过好像怎么样都不会让人联想到竹林啊。}}
|translation =Stage 2 theme       ※Composer: 11

A piece that is easygoing and free from start to end; the melody is especially free flowing.<br>Besides being easygoing, it also inherits the calmness of the previous stage.<br>The whole thing just became a piano melody somehow,<br>but there really isn't anything that makes one think of bamboo forests.
}}

