{{MusicRoom
|category =Stage 3 theme
|title    ={{lang|zh|木灵们的夏夜祭}}
|titleEN  =The Kodama's Summer Night Festival
|comment  ={{lang|zh|3面的主题曲。      ※作曲：11

进入三面，游戏也要逐渐热闹起来了。<br>在旋律上不了不少功夫，试着把钢琴做成了行云流水的样子<br>
在后面的风琴上，也尽量往旋律优美的方向去走。<br>才刚刚到三面而已啊，所以压制了一下过于激烈的感觉。}}

|translation = Stage 3 theme       ※Composer: 11

The game's getting livelier from this point on.<br>I spent a lot of effort on the melody trying to get the piano to have a constant flow going.<br>I also tried to steer the melody towards being beautiful during the organ part;<br>after all, it's only Stage 3, so I suppressed some of the excessive excitement.
}}

{{MusicRoom
|category =Stage 3 Boss - [[Shining Shooting Star/Characters#Seiryuu Sya|Seiryuu Sya]]'s theme
|title    ={{lang|zh|青柳传说}}
|titleEN  =Legend of the Willow Tree
|comment  ={{lang|zh|夏 青柳的主题曲。   ※作曲：11

突出了远离尘世，不沾俗气的纯净风格，气势也做很大。<br>试着使用了古风的元素，不过不是纯粹的古风。<br>面对这样一个设定，怎么能不倾注进感情来作曲呢？<br>于是，努力吧这首曲子编成了更加有故事，有情感的曲子。}}
|translation =Seiryuu Sya's theme       ※Composer: 11

A theme that tries to emphasize the feeling of being pure and untainted by the world. It sounds imposing as well.<br>I tried to incorporate some elements from ancient styles, but it's not just purely that;<br>after all, with a setting like this, how can I not pour in all my feelings?<br>Also, I tried to make this piece sound more story-like and expressive.
}}

