|translation =Kage Mimeima's theme       ※Composer: 11

When I set out to make this, the two styles that I first thought of were gloom and excitement, so I just mashed them together.<br>Perhaps putting more harmonious melodies would sound more beautiful being supported by strange melodies?<br>Triple time is too difficult.
}}

