Compared to the Extra Stage themes in Touhou, it feels lighter and less pressuring,<br>but the melodies are far from relaxed, and the tempo is not slow either.<br>After the intense battles in the main story, it's probably not bad to lighten up with a song like this.<br>Will the danmaku in the stage allow that though?
}}

