|translation =Rika Kirigakure's theme       ※Composer: 11

I tried to make it sound like a song from a “country in the east.”<br>The style is similar to Seiryuu's theme, but this one feels brighter.<br>I wanted to make it touch the listener's heart more, but I can't seem to convey the pressure of an Extra boss.<br>It's definitely the scholar's fault.
}}

